title: React Developer
description:
Required Skills & Qualifications

Strong proficiency in JavaScript (ES6+)

Hands-on experience with React.js and its core principles

Experience with HTML5, CSS3, and responsive design

Familiarity with RESTful APIs

Knowledge of state management libraries (Redux, Context API, etc.)

Experience with Git or other version control systems

Understanding of modern front-end build tools (Webpack, Babel, Vite)

title: AI Engineer
description:
Design, develop, and deploy machine learning and deep learning models

Build end-to-end AI pipelines: data preprocessing → training → evaluation → deployment

Work with LLMs, NLP, Computer Vision, or Predictive Models (based on use case)

Optimize models for performance, scalability, and cost

Integrate AI models with APIs, backend services, and applications

Monitor model performance and retrain models when required

Stay updated with the latest AI/ML research and industry trends

Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code
